{"tid":1813021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又有墮樓案, 十幾歲少女","createTime":"2020-01-06T03:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T04:52:26.000Z","uid":323373,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e53473401dec6aaff8d4f0a8cdc69022e1b60624","tid":1813021,"uid":323373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"1月6日蘋果突發:<br />\n大埔太和邨喜和樓，早上7時53分，一名女子由高處墮下，倒卧一樓平台，救護員接報到場，經檢驗後證實女事主當場不治。警方在平台搜證，正調查女事主身份及其墮樓原因。據了解，女事主年僅10多歲。 <br />\n<br />\n1月3日蘋果:<br />\n14歲女童蘇曉婷去年12月8日上午離開其位於二陂坊的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於去年12月12日向警方報案。<br />\n她身高約1.7米，體重約43公斤，瘦身材，長面型，黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿黑色上衣、黑色牛仔短褲及黑色和白色運動鞋。<br />\n<br />\n好担心係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa32d0f8d62eed692df4ef0d7e56d986477343c","tid":1813021,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"担<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131d5a66e7b3581de4fceea9ca033e401be16ef5","tid":1813021,"uid":149329,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"雖然off topic但係担你老母"},{"pid":"4ddab1b458de13bec00492ee8b4ba7d7cce014c9","tid":1813021,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65918fe27a9be8d70102a610d9f92f907fcf799f","tid":1813021,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ab36ecffc30bcf17119eadc76d7437b5fb7b6dd","tid":1813021,"uid":343323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"担<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla